    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically robust A80 chassis powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six. This unit remains true to its factory forced-induction architecture, paired with the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox known for its high torque capacity and precise gate engagement. The rear-end is equipped with the original Torsen limited-slip differential, providing excellent traction through corners. Recent maintenance includes a full timing belt service, new cam seals, and a valve clearance inspection to ensure the valvetrain remains within spec. The suspension features the original double-wishbone geometry with upgraded poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the paint exhibits minor road-going patina, the powertrain and structural integrity are dialed in for high-performance driving.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
