    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still in great shape! It runs like a dream and has been well-maintained over the years. You might find a few tiny signs of love here and there, but honestly, it\u2019s a fantastic ride that\u2019s got plenty of miles left in it. Perfect for commutes or weekend getaways! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
