    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul. The suspension retains its factory-intended kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. While showing honest signs of use, the drivetrain remains robust and the valvetrain is meticulously shimmed to factory specifications.",
